              "concept_source": "predicting feelings with 'will be + adjective'",
              "concept_target": "[TRANSLATE]",
              "explanation_source": "Use 'will be + adjective' to predict how someone will feel in the future. Common feeling adjectives include 'happy', 'unhappy', 'angry', 'glad'. Many negative feelings start with 'un-' (un-happy = not happy). 'Your neighbors will be unhappy' = the people next door are going to be displeased.",
